title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
